director.name: 谢里夫·科沃尔 Shariff Korver

trans_title: 菲尼克斯 第一季 第一季
introduction: A dark world of well-organised drug crime is hidden behind the calm life of Brabant. Jara and Rens both come to discover that when upon return to their birth province after a long time. She wants to clear the name of her father, he wants to distance himself from his criminal family - but they both get terribly entangled in the web of the upper and underworld, whose boundaries are becoming increasingly blurred.
chinese_title: 菲尼克斯 第一季 第一季
